{
    "@, you made it!": "ArchaeologyHouse_1848481_elliottReading_Elliott_event1",
    "I feel so relieved to be done with my book... it's like an elephant's been lifted off my shoulders.": "ArchaeologyHouse_1848481_elliottReading_Elliott_event1_sv1",
    "Well, I'd better get started with the reading... Wish me luck.": "ArchaeologyHouse_1848481_elliottReading_Elliott_event2",
    "Good afternoon, everyone.": "ArchaeologyHouse_1848481_elliottReading_Elliott_event3",
    "Hi!": "ArchaeologyHouse_1848481_elliottReading_Emily_textAboveHeadEvent1",
    "Ever since I was a young boy, I've dreamt of becoming a writer.": "ArchaeologyHouse_1848481_elliottReading_Elliott_event4",
    "When the time came for me to leave home and start my own life, I moved here. I was drawn to the peaceful beauty of the valley, and hoped that days of quiet reflection in this idyllic atmosphere would fan the literary flames.": "ArchaeologyHouse_1848481_elliottReading_Elliott_event4_sv1",
    "After countless hours scribbling at my writing desk, I present to you my first novel: 'The Rise And Fall Of Planet Yazzo'... It's a sci-fi epic spanning thousands of years in an exotic planetary system.": "ArchaeologyHouse_1848481_elliottReading_Elliott_event5",
    "Chapter One.": "ArchaeologyHouse_1848481_elliottReading_Elliott_event6",
    "Commander Yutkin stepped through the golden archway as the airlock snapped shut behind him. Today was his first day on Planet Yazzo, and all 14 of the alliance delegates had been summoned to the Grand Spire...": "ArchaeologyHouse_1848481_elliottReading_Elliott_event6_sv1",
    "...And as the 7th moon descended beneath the horizon, the planet of Yazzo would begin its sinister transformation... an event for which Commander Yutkin was completely unprepared.": "ArchaeologyHouse_1848481_elliottReading_Elliott_event7",
    "Well, that concludes my reading. I'll be selling signed copies of the book by the front desk. Thanks for listening!": "ArchaeologyHouse_1848481_elliottReading_Elliott_event8",
    "Well, how was it?": "ArchaeologyHouse_1848481_elliottReading_Elliott_event9",
    "Thanks.": "ArchaeologyHouse_1848481_elliottReading_Elliott_event10",
    "You know, I got the idea for making a sci-fi book from you. Do you remember?": "ArchaeologyHouse_1848481_elliottReading_Elliott_event10_sv1",
    "That's why I've dedicated this book to you...": "ArchaeologyHouse_1848481_elliottReading_Elliott_event10_sv2"
}